    ('"Mine husband is innocent, I know it!. He intended to buy the fruit. Why must I join thy society in order for me to be taken at my word?"', '「我丈夫是無辜的，我知道！他原本是想買水果的。為什麼我必須加入你們的社團，你們才肯相信我的話？」'),
