    ('case "accused" attend labelFunc04A9_016E:', 'case "指控" attend labelFunc04A9_016E:'),
    ('"They say if I join they will attempt to free mine husband. But it was they who unjustly accused him. I cannot trust them, but I fear I may have no choice."', '「他們說如果我加入，他們會試圖釋放我丈夫。但是他們不公正地指控了他。我無法信任他們，但我擔心我可能別無選擇。」'),
